  "body": "<p>Hi there ! <a href=\"http://olennka-handmade.blogspot.com/\">Olennka</a> here. I love giving gifts. I always want to give something special to my friends and family. I also want to make it as much handmade as it's possible. Wrapping gifts is very important for me and I try to this with all my heart. I decided to make my own wrapping paper. Here's very simple way how to do this.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598256677636-UHONE05GVVNCTXNDCKKN/7a-DIY%2Bstamped%2Bwrapping%2Bpaper.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>You need just plain grey or white paper and ink pad and some stamps. I used Amy's stamps, they are just perfect for this.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"7b-DIY+stamped+wrapping+paper.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598256711872-IKZGXGJWSZG07BYSADCO/7b-DIY%2Bstamped%2Bwrapping%2Bpaper.jpeg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"7c-DIY+stamped+wrapping+paper.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598256711933-I2KVDZ2AU8SDN5NYRD71/7c-DIY%2Bstamped%2Bwrapping%2Bpaper.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Now stamp some patterns , wrap your present. Make tags with name, I used Die Cuts Chipboard and cardstock shapes from STITCHED collection and voila perfect Valentine's gift is ready. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598256731167-C0SUJL2WLR0IJW8BPJ4B/7d-DIY%2Bstamped%2Bwrapping%2Bpaper.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><em>Absolutely wonderful wrapping! Thanks for sharing, </em><a href=\"http://olennka-handmade.blogspot.com/\"><em>Olennka</em></a><em>! Shop for Amy Tangerine products at your local scrapbook stores and online at </em><a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=simon%20home%20page&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom\"><em>Simon Says Stamp</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=213361&amp;m=25838&amp;afftrack=Amy%20tangerine&amp;urllink=www%2Ebluemoonscrapbooking%2Ecom%2FCategoryProductList%2Ejsp%3Fcat%3DShop%253AManufacturers%253AAmerican%2BCrafts%3AAmerican%2BCrafts%2BAmy%2BTangerine\"><em>Blue Moon Scrapbooking</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=33086&amp;m=7429&amp;afftrack=&amp;urllink=store%2Escrapbook%2Ecom%2Fproducts%2F%3Fw%3Damy%2Btangerine\"><em>Scrapbook.com</em></a><em>. </em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
